<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2020-04-06</DATELINE><TITLE>Pangolins Harbor SARS-CoV-2-Related Coronaviruses</TITLE><BODY>The pandemic of coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) caused by SARS-CoV-2 has posed a severe threat to global public health. Yet, the origin of SARS-CoV-2 remains mysterious. Several recent studies (e.g., Lam et al ., Xiao et al .) identified SARS-CoV-2-related viruses in pangolins, providing novel insights into the evolution and diversity of SARS-CoV-2-related viruses.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>